{"tid":783080,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過心跳太快扎醒左","createTime":"2018-08-17T09:36:43.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-18T12:11:38.000Z","uid":86809,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"13cdc67aab5ba4914b914fb2cf4a4557614fed3e","tid":783080,"uid":86809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:36:43.000Z","msg":"尋晚通左晚頂<br />\n今朝早訓左個零鐘左右突然扎撚醒左<br />\n個感覺係成個人比人係夢入面格硬拉左出黎<br />\n起左身成個人好唔舒服<br />\n維持左成幾分鐘<br />\n第一次遇到d咁既情況唔識形容<br />\n係直情成個人想衝出窗跳落街個種難受<br />\n之後一摸下個心<br />\n仆街 1秒跳成3 4下到<br />\n係梳化冷靜左一輪先落返120左右<br />\n一路到而家唔撚敢訓<br />\n點撚算好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34d93d7667d5072506be24b19ca1f36f41ad12fa","tid":783080,"uid":89857,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:40:33.000Z","msg":"沒事兒 沒事兒"},{"pid":"afc8db931df5314b5def3dddc9d5835bc036c83b","tid":783080,"uid":74262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:44:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"099bd137fd56c4010abd87fd8e356430286ce013","tid":783080,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"醒左都好似仲係惡夢咁"},{"pid":"3fe05c286cb0996ee4696daae07e2fd240ecc62c","tid":783080,"uid":38793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"睇醫生"},{"pid":"56f77c08990c6964beec0681bf07179cd3a274c6","tid":783080,"uid":86809,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"099bd137fd56c4010abd87fd8e356430286ce013","tid":783080,"uid":32263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:44:54.000Z","msg":"醒左都好似仲係惡夢咁"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:48:04.000Z","msg":"屌巴打你明我講緊咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"938163a2da8b292f8ce0a2c7c44ea72b606c4726","tid":783080,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-17T09:49:25.000Z","msg":"睡窒息症?"},{"pid":"00305b36ff8cb16dbdce65dacda6fb54d3601786","tid":78